code formulation for vl_code fields

vl_code is an integer of at list 4 digits.
first 3 represent a table prefix
last 3 are in table unique values.


* Global tables *  
11 vl_precision
12 vl_remote
13 vl_status
14 vl_visible
15 vl_watertype

* Installation related *
